rows.label: qev031102_MSG0001
rows.name: Hmm. Is this another Earth plant?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0002
rows.name:
Fascinating. Might I cut one down to bring home?
I wish to use it in my research.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev031102_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask the Orphean if he is a botanist.

rows.label: qev031102_JNK0020
rows.name: Deny

rows.label: qev031102_SEL0021
rows.name: Inform the Orphean that the trees are public property.

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0003
rows.name:
Yes, I trade in the compositional analysis and
reproduction of plants.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0004
rows.name: And you are...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0005
rows.name:
Ah, I see. You seek information on how to best raise
a tree species brought to Mira by one of the Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0006
rows.name:
Well, any typical tree can be made to grow by using
gnarlbranch sap—which can be found in the vicinity
of the Divine Roost at the north edge of Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0007
rows.name: I am curious to see this Great Tree for myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0008
rows.name:
My Ovah has begun to throb as well. So be it.
I will meet with this Prone woman.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0009
rows.name:
You treat such organisms as public property?
You humans are as odd as I had initially suspected.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0010
rows.name:
But very well. As residents of New LA,
we must abide by your rules.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0011
rows.name:
A seed of that type should mature quickly if treated
with gnarlbranch sap from the Divine Roost at the
north edge of Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0012
rows.name:
Mmm... I cannot wait. This Great Tree seems to be
a species very much to my taste.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0013
rows.name: Kindly deliver the gnarlbranch sap to Naza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0014
rows.name:
I am eager to see what manner of plant this Great Tree
grows into.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0015
rows.name:
I have consumed something which for her bears the
same significance as my Ovah.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0016
rows.name:
Truly, it was a grave mistake. Please secure the two
materials I have requested, and I will restore the
Great Tree without hesitation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0017
rows.name:
Have you acquired the materials needed to regenerate
the Great Tree?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0018
rows.name: Ah, just as I requested. I will begin work at once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0019
rows.name:
In the interest of precision, Naza, I need to ask a
number of questions about this Great Tree of yours.
Do you find this acceptable?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0020
rows.name:
You may ask. But make haste.
If tree is lost, so are you, Professor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0021
rows.name:
Rest assured that your knowledge—combined with
the data I acquired by consuming the tree—should
prove most sufficient.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0022
rows.name:
Now, if I may. Please describe the history you Prone
share with these sacred trees...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0023
rows.name: ...He did it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0024
rows.name:
I assert that this reconstruction is a perfect match for
the Great Trees your people have long worshiped.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0025
rows.name:
Hmm... You know? Seen in this light, I can
understand why one might think these trees
are hosts to the divine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0026
rows.name:
Professor is strange. Not bad. But strange.
...But other races often are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0027
rows.name:
Maybe races just need to speak to each other.
What do you think, Earth alien?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_JNK0030
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev031102_SEL0031
rows.name: Nod in agreement.

rows.label: qev031102_JNK0040
rows.name: Caution

rows.label: qev031102_SEL0041
rows.name: Warn Naza that perfect understanding is impossible.

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0028
rows.name: You are wise, Earth alien. Credit to your race.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0029
rows.name:
I will learn from your example.
I will be less quick to violence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0030
rows.name: Perhaps this is true.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0031
rows.name:
Cavern Clan are Prone. Tree Clan are Prone.
Yet we have fought for 10,000 suns.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0032
rows.name: But maybe my clan can join Orphe in peace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0033
rows.name:
You ate Great Tree, then made new Great Tree.
You taught how to make it grow strong.
We are even now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0034
rows.name: Huh?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0035
rows.name: Yun'tonam? What are you doing here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0036
rows.name:
I came at the guidance of my Ovah. I sensed you
were creating a palatable tree and came to dine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0037
rows.name: You... YOU! That was my Great Tree![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0038
rows.name: Hmm? This tree's original was a possession of yours?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0039
rows.name:
Well, your Prone tree was very much to my liking.
I hope to enjoy another soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0040
rows.name: Grk! GWAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0041
rows.name: Here. Take reward.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0042
rows.name:
I will speak to this new Orphean.
Speak until we reach understanding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0043
rows.name:
Very...thorough...understanding.
By any means necessary![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0044
rows.name:
You need not thank me. And if you require further
Great Tree copies, you have only to ask.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0045
rows.name:
Also thanks to you, Earth alien. If not for you,
this would have ended in disaster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031102_MSG0046
rows.name: Take this as symbol of my thanks.[ST:wait ]
